Package: FlorestaR
Title: Forest Dynamics Simulation and 3D Visualization
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Mateus", "Pinheiro", 
           email = "mateus.opinheiro@hotmail.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An integrated tool for simulating forest growth, mortality, and recruitment 
    using Artificial Neural Networks. It features 3D forest rendering, a management 
    interface for logging scenarios, and time-lapse animations of forest evolution 
    to support sustainable forest management decisions.
License: GPL (>= 3)
